# next-15-app-router-host-app

For the SDK testing within the NextJS@15 + App router

Additional setup:
- in `entrypoint.sh` the `@types/react@17` is additionally injected to the SDK's `package.json` file to reproduce the `@types/react` conflict withing the SDK and the host app.
  - because of the `@types/react@17` is installed to the local to SDK `node_modules` directory and it conflicts with the `@types/react@18` required by the host app itself.
  - to validate proper types for all exported from SDK components, this app has a special page where all SDK components are used
